jimjams.airmonitor.datastructure

Class Snapshot

  • java.lang.Object
    • jimjams.airmonitor.datastructure.Snapshot

  • public class Snapshot
extends Object
    Captures instantaneous environmental data and associates it with a personal Ecological Momentary Assessment (EMA).

      • Snapshot

        public Snapshot(List<SensorData> data,
                List<String> conditions,
                EcologicalMomentaryAssessment ema,
                Context context)
        Constructor. The location will be set to null if it cannot be resolved via the Context.
        Parameters:
        data - Array of SensorData at the time of the Snapshot
        conditions - Existing conditions at the time of the Snapshot
        ema - EMA at the time of the Snapshot
        context - The context to be used to fetch the location. Generally, this is just the invoking Activity.
